263
00:15:50,865 --> 00:15:54,465
Tapi masih banyak yang harus kau pelajari, detektif pengelana.

264
00:15:54,465 --> 00:15:55,465
Hah?

265
00:15:55,465 --> 00:15:58,965
Jahe memang mengandung protease,

266
00:15:58,965 --> 00:16:02,265
