342
00:20:19,465 --> 00:20:21,965
Mungkin istriku.

343
00:20:21,965 --> 00:20:23,565
Tentu, silahkan.

344
00:20:23,565 --> 00:20:25,665
Terima kasih.

345
00:20:26,565 --> 00:20:29,065
Halo, sayang?

346
00:20:29,065 --> 00:20:33,665
Restoran tempat kita berada memiliki Romanee-Conti antik.

347
00:20:33,665 --> 00:20:36,665
Bisakah aku mentraktir orang tuaku?

